{
    "headline": "Vermicelli Noodle Bowl",
    "name": "Vermicelli Noodle Bowl",
    "description": "This vermicelli bowl combines rice noodles, cucumber, bean sprouts, herbs, shrimp, and a sweet-and-sour sauce for a very delicious Vietnamese salad.",
